item.description:
This is the biweekly meetup time for us to get together and discuss the events in the area, successes, review the plan for the coming weeks, and allocate resources to events and strategies. Everyone is invited.

Agenda -
7:00 - 7:15: last week's activities. field plan Rich, Brooke
7:15 - 7:30: progress on last week's action items
7:30 - 7:45: plans for next week/this week activities, inc. training Brooke, Joan
7:45 open discussion

Thanks!

We are collecting donations for meetup activities and materials. Please give what you can.
item.name: Nashua Meetup Planning Session
